    "body": "The `autocomplete=off` actually means the native autocomplete you can see in any text box, this is disabled here because it often colludes with what users actually want to type. If you want to use autocomplete on a searchbox, this is the simplest way to do it: \r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/rlp0m6yp",
